          'Research Design & Data: Describe the methodology (quantitative, qualitative, or mixed), data sources (administrative records, panel surveys, case studies, interviews with officials), and analytical strategy.',
          'Findings: Present results clearly, using tables for regression outputs, thematic summaries for qualitative data, or comparative case narratives as appropriate to the method.',
